{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Block","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Block","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>术语 <strong>block</strong> 在不同的上下文中有多种含义。这些含义可能是</p><dl>\n\n    <dt id=\"block_css\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Block/CSS\">Block (CSS)</a></dt>\n    <dd>网页上的区块指的是出现在新行上的 HTML element，即在该元素的前一个元素的下方，在后一个元素之上（通常称为块级元素）。例如，HTML 中的 <code>p</code> 元素默认是<em>块级元素</em>，而 <code>a</code> 元素是一个<em>内联元素</em> - 你可以在 HTML 源码中将多个标记紧挨着写在一起，渲染结果是，它们将在同一行显示。</dd>\n\n    <dt id=\"block_块作用域\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Block/Scripting\">Block (块作用域)</a></dt>\n    <dd>在 JavaScript中，函数块是指被大括号 (\"{}\") 包裹住的相关联的statement的集合。例如，你可以在 <code>Statements/if...else</code>后声明一段函数块形式的代码，表明当条件判断为真时，解释程序应该运行上述函数块里的代码，或者当条件判断为假时跳过执行上述函数块里的代码。</dd>\n\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"术语 block 在不同的上下文中有多种含义。这些含义可能是","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Block","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Block","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Bloc","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Block (ブロック)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Block","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Block","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Блок","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Block","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/block","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/block/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Block","title":"Block"}],"pageTitle":"Block - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}